---
syntax: powershell
tags: [ ad, domain ]
---

## Check if local machine has secure channel with domain
Test-ComputerSecureChannel

## Check if local machine has secure channel with specific domain server
Test-ComputerSecureChannel -Server "DCName.fabrikam.com"

## Repair secure channel with domain
Test-ComputerSecureChannel -Repair

## Reset password for local computer against specific domain controller
Reset-ComputerMachinePassword -Server "DC01" -Credential Domain01\Admin01